I usually order half chicken w rice and bean. Chicken is always fresh and tasty. Just out of the oven. But there is a thing. Chicken breast is dry, and tasteless. That’s normal. I understand it, that’s what chicken is like. Thighs are tasty and softer than breast. So I suggest you to tear chicken breast to small prices and mix it with their sauce. It will taste better. They have different food everyday, you will never get bored.

(Translated by Google) The customer service is incredibly bad, on different occasions, I have ordered here and sometimes my food arrives and other times they cancel it after waiting up to an hour and they don't even explain the reason, until you call them and they tell you that your address is far away, which does not make any sense because otherwise it should not appear in the delivery range ... Also, how is it that sometimes they send my delivery and sometimes not? I gave them 5 chances at different times and it's still the same! There are no excuses The only kind person who works there is a Good Men, when the ladies attend they don't even care to give a solution and they blame the person from the Delivery!  It's sad, because their food is not bad, but it is useless if they do not care about their customers and have such bad attention!
